 boiling","150 g sultanas","200 g carrots, cut in slices (2 mm)","200 g courgettes, cut in slices (2 mm)"]}],"id":"r84722","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-Xhr3B5sI1BM\/XZQxoP5VUOI\/AAAAAAAAcw4\/3qZMCzc2tnw2zgygvPwKWx0aUy1RAXN2gCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_wiwqAIxGI3aksndQ.png","title":"Moroccan Lamb with Couscous","publishedAt":"2015-05-13T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"29.9 g","fat":"23.3 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"56.6 g","calories":"2324 kJ \/ 556 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, bowl, aluminium foil, jug, large serving plate","basicInfo":["medium","35m","50m","6 portions"]}